    <p>And the dramas he had read so often regained their original magic when he replaced the imaginary protagonists with people he knew in real life, reserving for himself and Fermina Daza the roles of <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="star-crossed lovers | star-crossed - not favored by the stars, ILL-FATED, e.g. a pair of star-crossed lovers take their life"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(阴差阳错的恋人)</code></b>.</p>
