  <li>
    <p>And he <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="committed the calculated impertinence"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(做出故意的无礼行为)</code></b> of changing his seat in the dining room so that he would face her.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>And then he took the step he had not dared to take during the preceding days: he waved goodbye to Rosalba, and the three women responded in kind, with a familiarity that <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="cut him to the quick"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(深深伤害/刺痛)</code></b> because his boldness came too late.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Then he felt alone in the world, and the memory of Fermina Daza, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="lying in ambush"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(藏在暗中)</code></b> in recent days, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="dealt him a mortal blow"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(给了他致命的一击)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>On the contrary, the more he <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="delved into"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(探索/查考)</code></b> the search the further he felt from the truth.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>And so the most difficult hours passed for him, at times in the person of a timid prince or a paladin of love, at other times <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="in his own scalded hide of a lover in the middle of forgetting"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(回到他伤痕累累的皮囊，变成一个被遗忘的恋人)</code></b>, until the first breezes began to blow and he went to doze in the lounge chairs by the railings.</p>
  </li>
